Quickstrike:





Quickstrile felt the missiles go by him as his body went into a near laying 
down possition. He went dazed for a while, then a pain hit his shoulder. He 
screamed and went for his shoulder. He felt something at it and yanked it 
off. Whatever was between the jaws of his cobra hand, he slammed it into the 
floor and pinned it there.

Quickstrike was in the process of panicing.
